dex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xyt1665703024880.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xyt1665703024880.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xyt1665703024880.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xyt1665703024880\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Derived Component Entity\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Derived Component Entity is a Development Object that references and inherits from a Modeled Entity. It has a Component or Modeled Component as parent object. It is used for the component's database I/O, data presentation, and inter-component communication.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__section_cn3_tlq_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d764735e51\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__image_rth_wlq_lwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/component_entity_modeled2_28bfc407b71b2e52dcf4790acd6d9797.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ent</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifc1665702608950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifc1665702608950.html\" title=\"A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data.\">Component</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vfj1665703025321.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfj1665703025321.html\" title=\"A Modeled Component is a Component that can be used to create derived components, which inherit the component-level properties, code containers, and constants from the modeled component.\">Modeled Component</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zyj1665702550619.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zyj1665702550619.html\" title=\"A Component Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in a Component Entity.\">Component Field</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyt1665702609153.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyt1665702609153.html\" title=\"A Label is a Development Object that contains text that appears on a presentation component. Labels have properties, but most cannot be set dynamically.\">Label</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"byl1665703025171.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/byl1665703025171.html\" title=\"A Derived Entity is a Development Object that references and inherits from a Modeled Entity. It can be a subobject of a Modeled Entity (in which case it is known as a Subtype Entity), or of a Component or Modeled Component.\">Derived Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xyt1665703024880__table_d10502e1_d10503e1_d10504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>/ent:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ModeledEntityName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__section_npj_xlq_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d764735e309\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__p_d94898e1_d94899e1_d94900e1\">A derived entity specializes Component Entity in the\n        following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__ul_rnd_zlq_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__li_d37199e1_d37200e1_d37201e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__p_d94901e1_d94902e1_d94903e1\">It references a Modeled Entity.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__li_d37202e1_d37203e1_d37204e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__p_d94904e1_d94905e1_d94906e1\">It initially inherits its properties and code\n            containers from the Modeled Entity. Changes in the Modeled Entity are applied to the\n            derived entity when the Component is compiled, unless the property or code has been\n            changed in the Component.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__li_d37205e1_d37206e1_d37207e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xyt1665703024880__p_d94907e1_d94908e1_d94909e1\">The fields of the Modeled Entity are not\n            inherited—they can be explicitly added as Component Fields.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617097\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617097\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Derived Component Entity Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Derived Component Entity A Derived Component Entity is a Development Object that references and inherits from a Modeled Entity. It has a Component or Modeled Component as parent object. It is used for the component's database I/O, data presentation, and inter-component communication. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: ent Main Development Object? No Part of: Component , Modeled Component , Component Entity Contains: Component Entity , Component Field , Label , Property , Code Container Generalization: Component Entity , Derived Entity Specializations: — Compilation Output: — URI format: cpt: ComponentName /ent: ModeledEntityName Specialization A derived entity specializes Component Entity in the following ways: It references a Modeled Entity. It initially inherits its properties and code containers from the Modeled Entity. Changes in the Modeled Entity are applied to the derived entity when the Component is compiled, unless the property or code has been changed in the Component. The fields of the Modeled Entity are not inherited—they can be explicitly added as Component Fields. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}